class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   成功时返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.true">true</a></span></strong>， 或者在失败时返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.ftp-rmdir-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <table class="doctable informaltable">       <thead>     <tr>      <th>版本</th>      <th>说明</th>     </tr>    </thead>    <tbody class="tbody">     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">ftp</span> 参数接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ftp-connection.php" class="classname">FTP\Connection</a></span>  实例，之前接受 <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div>  <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.ftp-rmdir-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-4557">    <p><strong>示例 #1 <span class="function"><strong>ftp_rmdir()</strong></span> 示例</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>\$dir </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'www/'</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 简单基本连接<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$ftp </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">ftp_connect</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$ftp_server</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 使用用户名和密码进行登录<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$login_result </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">ftp_login</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$ftp</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$ftp_user_name</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$ftp_user_pass</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br><br></span><span style="color: #FF8000">// 尝试删除 \$dir 目录<br></span><span style="color: #007700">if (</span><span style="color: #9876AA">ftp_rmdir</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$ftp</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$dir</span><span style="color: #007700">)) {<br>    echo </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Successfully deleted </span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$dir</span><span style="color: #DD0000">\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br>} else {<br>    echo </span><span style="color: #DD0000">"There was a problem while deleting </span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$dir</span><span style="color: #DD0000">\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br>}<br><br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">ftp_close</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">\$ftp</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br><br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.ftp-rmdir-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link ftp_mkdir()} - 建立新目录</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
